      "content" : [
        {
          "anchor" : "Overview",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Overview",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "This documentation is specific to hosting on GitHub Pages but the steps",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "should apply to most static hosting solutions you’re familiar with.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Configure-GitHub-Pages",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Configure GitHub Pages",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Begin by following",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier" : "https:\/\/docs.github.com\/pages\/getting-started-with-github-pages\/configuring-a-publishing-source-for-your-github-pages-site#choosing-a-publishing-source",
              "isActive" : true,
              "type" : "reference"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "to enable GitHub pages on your repository and select a publishing source.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "You can choose to either publish from your ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "main",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " branch alongside your project’s source code",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "or a specific branch that you’ll use exclusively for your GitHub pages site.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Either way, you should choose the option to publish from the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "\/docs",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "subdirectory instead of the default option to publish from your repository’s root.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Next, clone the repository you just configured for GitHub pages and checkout",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "the branch you chose as a publishing source.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code" : [
            "$ git clone [repository-url]",
            "$ cd [repository-name]",
            "$ git checkout [gh-pages-branch]"
          ],
          "syntax" : "shell",
          "type" : "codeListing"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Understanding-your-Project’s-Configuration",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Understanding your Project’s Configuration",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Now that you’ve set up a local clone of the repository you’ll be publishing documentation from,",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "you can build your Swift-DocC documentation site.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "content" : [
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "Before invoking the Swift-DocC plugin, you’ll need to add it as a dependency of your package,",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "see ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "identifier" : "doc:\/\/SwiftDocCPlugin\/documentation\/SwiftDocCPlugin\/Getting-Started-with-the-Swift-DocC-Plugin",
                  "isActive" : true,
                  "type" : "reference"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " for details.",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "style" : "tip",
          "type" : "aside"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Before running the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "swift package generate-documentation",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " command, you’ll need to know two things.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items" : [
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "What is the ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "inlineContent" : [
                        {
                          "text" : "base path",
                          "type" : "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type" : "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " your documentation will be published at?",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "This differs based on the",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier" : "https:\/\/docs.github.com\/pages\/getting-started-with-github-pages\/about-github-pages#types-of-github-pages-sites",
                      "isActive" : true,
                      "type" : "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : "",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : "but is ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "inlineContent" : [
                        {
                          "text" : "almost",
                          "type" : "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type" : "emphasis"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " always the name of your GitHub repository.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Your documentation site will be published at something like",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "code" : [
                    "https:\/\/<username>.github.io\/<repository-name>"
                  ],
                  "syntax" : "txt",
                  "type" : "codeListing"
                },
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "and Swift-DocC needs to know about any base path after the ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code" : "github.io",
                      "type" : "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " portion in order",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : "to correctly configure relative links. In the above case, that would be ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code" : "<repository-name>",
                      "type" : "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : ".",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content" : [
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Which ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "inlineContent" : [
                        {
                          "text" : "target",
                          "type" : "text"
                        }
                      ],
                      "type" : "strong"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " in your Swift Package would you like to publish documentation for?",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "inlineContent" : [
                    {
                      "text" : "Swift-DocC can build documentation for a single target at a time. When publishing documentation,",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : " ",
                      "type" : "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "text" : "you should select one target per documentation site.",
                      "type" : "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type" : "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type" : "orderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "Once you’ve determined your hosting ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "base path",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "strong"
            },
            {
              "text" : " and Swift Package ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "target",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "strong"
            },
            {
              "text" : ", you’re ready to",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "generate documentation.",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "anchor" : "Generating-the-Documentation-Site",
          "level" : 2,
          "text" : "Generating the Documentation Site",
          "type" : "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent" : [
            {
              "text" : "To build documentation for your site and send the output to the ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "code" : "\/docs",
              "type" : "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text" : " directory at the root",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : " ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "text" : "of the repository you cloned to host your documentation, run the following ",
              "type" : "text"
            },
            {
              "inlineContent" : [
                {
                  "text" : "from the root",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : " ",
                  "type" : "text"
                },
                {
                  "text" : "of the Swift package you want to generate documentation from",
                  "type" : "text"
                }
              ],
              "type" : "strong"
            },
            {
              "text" : ":",
              "type" : "text"
            }
          ],
          "type" : "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "code" : [
            "$ swift package --allow-writing-to-directory [path-to-docs-directory] \\",
            "    generate-documentation --target [target-name] \\",
            "    --disable-indexing \\",
            "    --transform-for-static-hosting \\",
            "    --hosting-base-path [hosting-base-path] \\",
            "    --output-path [path-to-docs-directory]"
          ],
          "syntax" : "shell",
          "type" : "codeListing"
        },
        {
